source.name: Energy Usage Analysis System
source.description: The EUAS application is a web based system which serves Energy Center of Expertise, under the Office of Facilitates Management and Service Programs.  EUAS is used for tracking energy details for various energy sources namely electricity, natural gas, oil, chilled water, steam and renewable energy.
